<text top="2053" left="1561" width="587" height="50" font="font7" id="p1_t119" reading_order_no="118" segment_no="5" tag_type="text">Mbeki  was  desperate  to  demonstrate </text>
<text top="2096" left="1510" width="629" height="50" font="font7" id="p1_t120" reading_order_no="119" segment_no="5" tag_type="text">that  this  was  an  African  initiative.  Any </text>
<text top="2138" left="1511" width="667" height="53" font="font3" id="p1_t121" reading_order_no="120" segment_no="5" tag_type="text">hint  that  he  was  doing  the  West’s  bidding </text>
