<text top="2224" left="1510" width="619" height="53" font="font3" id="p1_t123" reading_order_no="122" segment_no="5" tag_type="text">The  anticolonial  struggle,  though  won </text>
<text top="2271" left="1511" width="651" height="51" font="font4" id="p1_t124" reading_order_no="123" segment_no="5" tag_type="text">over  half  a  century  ago  in  most  of Africa, </text>
<text top="2312" left="1511" width="629" height="54" font="font8" id="p1_t125" reading_order_no="124" segment_no="5" tag_type="text">remains  one  of  the  few  unifying  causes </text>
<text top="2358" left="1511" width="278" height="51" font="font4" id="p1_t126" reading_order_no="125" segment_no="5" tag_type="text">for  the  continent. </text>
<text top="2405" left="1562" width="586" height="46" font="font5" id="p1_t127" reading_order_no="126" segment_no="6" tag_type="text">Zimbabwe,  of  course,  did  not  sign  up </text>
<text top="2445" left="1511" width="659" height="53" font="font3" id="p1_t128" reading_order_no="127" segment_no="6" tag_type="text">to  be  reviewed,  and  no  mechanism  exists </text>
<text top="2490" left="1511" width="664" height="54" font="font8" id="p1_t129" reading_order_no="128" segment_no="6" tag_type="text">to  hold  it  to  account.  The  unfolding  battle </text>
<text top="2535" left="1511" width="649" height="51" font="font4" id="p1_t130" reading_order_no="129" segment_no="6" tag_type="text">for  its  political  soul,  however,  is  a  test  for </text>
<text top="2579" left="1510" width="663" height="51" font="font4" id="p1_t131" reading_order_no="130" segment_no="6" tag_type="text">the  whole  continent.  Will  its  rulers  stand </text>
<text top="2622" left="1510" width="644" height="50" font="font7" id="p1_t132" reading_order_no="131" segment_no="6" tag_type="text">by  the  principles  they  have  signed  up  to, </text>
<text top="2664" left="1511" width="659" height="51" font="font4" id="p1_t133" reading_order_no="132" segment_no="6" tag_type="text">or  will  Mugabe’s  personal  stature  and  his </text>
<text top="2710" left="1511" width="641" height="50" font="font7" id="p1_t134" reading_order_no="133" segment_no="6" tag_type="text">anti-Western  rhetoric  trump  these  prin- </text>
<text top="2753" left="1511" width="662" height="51" font="font4" id="p1_t135" reading_order_no="134" segment_no="6" tag_type="text">ciples?  This  is  a  defining  moment  not  just </text>
<text top="2796" left="1511" width="456" height="51" font="font4" id="p1_t136" reading_order_no="135" segment_no="6" tag_type="text">for  Zimbabwe  but  for  Africa. </text>
